BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260322T090600
DTEND:20260322T124800
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.001ft at 09:06\n-2.986ft at 12:48\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Decent size blend of mid-period SSW swell and secondary NW swell has surf 
 mainly running thigh-waist-stomach high. Dawn patrol is drained by a negat
 ive low tide\, then the early afternoon high tide slows down the smaller s
 urf. \n\nWinds are light/variable in the morning\, light southerly onshore
  for the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
