BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260323T071200
DTEND:20260323T074200
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.428ft at 07:12\n-0.052ft at 07:42\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Smaller combo of SSW swell and NW swell rolling in with mainly thigh to wa
 ist high waves. Early morning is drained by a negative low tide\, then the
  mid afternoon high tide bogs down tide sensitive breaks. Some new\, steep
 -angled NW swell shows over the afternoon to bump up best exposures a litt
 le towards the end of the day. \n\nLight/variable morning winds are expect
 ed to be followed by light afternoon SW-S onshores. 
END:VEVENT
