BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260324T070600
DTEND:20260324T085400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.628ft at 07:06\n-0.008ft at 08:54\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 New round of fair size SW Southern Hemi fills in\, as secondary NW swell l
 ingers. By the afternoon good southerly exposures are running waist to sho
 ulder high\, while focal points hit head high\, largest late. Mid morning 
 drained by a negative low tide.\n\nAt this point the call is for light off
 shores in the morning\, turning to light southerly onshores over the after
 noon. 
END:VEVENT
