DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.933ft at 07:06\n-0.054ft at 10:00\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Blend of long-period SW swell and steep-angled\, shorter-period NW swell i
 s scheduled to rise through the day\, with waves getting into the chest-sh
 oulder-head high range at better breaks over the afternoon\, showing large
 st late. Mid day negative low tide drains most spots. \n\nNNW winds due th
 rough the day\, keeping town spots offshore. 
END:VEVENT
